name: Another heartache
description: That day, around 08:00 AM John just woke up from a long dream last night. He hoped that today would be as beautiful as the previous day, an activity that was carried out so perfectly by listening to music through plates, cassette tapes, and radio. John did it day after day. But something was different that day, a thing happened that made John feel unbearable pain, namely because one of his cassette tape collections was damaged, he said quietly "It turns out that not only because of love I can be hurt, but because of this too!" .
